Package jellycat.flight.domain.dao

Class DaoFlight

  • java.lang.Object
    • jellycat.flight.domain.dao.DaoFlight
  • public class DaoFlight
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds a collection of airports from airports described in XML Parses an XML string to read each of the airports and adds each valid airport to the collection. The method uses Java DOM (Document Object Model) to convert from XML to Java primitives. Method iterates over the set of Airport nodes in the XML string and builds an Airport object from the XML node string and add the Airport object instance to the Airports collection.
    Since:
    2019-04-20
    Version:

        public static Flights addAll​(java.lang.String xmlFlights)
                      throws java.lang.NullPointerException
        Builds a collection of airports from airports described in XML Parses an XML string to read each of the airports and adds each valid airport to the collection. The method uses Java DOM (Document Object Model) to convert from XML to Java primitives. Method iterates over the set of Airport nodes in the XML string and builds an Airport object from the XML node string and add the Airport object instance to the Airports collection.
        Parameters:
        xmlFlights - XML string containing set of airports
        Returns:
        [possibly empty] collection of Airports in the xml string
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - included to keep signature consistent with other addAll methods
